      <abstract>
        <label>Abstract</label>
        <p>The presence in New Zealand of the triozid <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Casuarinicola</tp:taxon-name-part> <tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">australis</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> Taylor, 2010 is reported for the first time, based on new material from Auckland. This is also the first record of the genus from New Zealand.</p>
      </abstract>
